body_html:
@cancan101 : That is an informational log line, not an error. That logging line has been there for a while, so I'm surprised that you're seeing it only now. Perhaps your logs were being redirected somewhere else before and you didn't notice them?

Regardless, this shouldn't be causing any problems. Is it?
